Goal
Implement reliable automated backend tests for services, repositories, controllers, security, and critical integrations.

Scope
Included: backend/wsms Spring Boot module
Excluded: frontend tests
Checklist
Foundation
        Standardize Maven test dependencies
        Add JUnit 5 + Mockito stack
        Add coverage tooling and thresholds
        Add test profile configuration
        Define test naming conventions
Unit Tests
        AuthService tests
        UserService tests
        ServerService tests
        PasswordResetService tests
        SignupVerificationService tests
        AlertService tests
        MetricService tests
Repository Tests
        UserRepository query tests
        ServerRepository query tests
        MetricRepository query tests
        RequestLogRepository query tests
Controller Tests
        AuthController
        UserController
        ServerController
        MetricController
        AlertController
        RequestLogController
        Admin controllers
Security Tests
        SecurityConfig authorization matrix
        JwtAuthenticationFilter token behavior
        CustomUserDetailsService user loading
Integration Tests
        Signup to login flow
        Server management flow
        Metric ingest and fetch flow
        AOP logging smoke coverage
        WebSocket terminal auth handshake
CI and Quality
        CI runs tests on every PR
        Coverage threshold enforced
        Flaky test handling policy
        Bugfix requires regression test
Success Criteria
        Critical endpoints and services covered
        Security paths verified
        CI green and stable
        Coverage target achieved